data.title: Ponte di Verzuno (Rio Rivaletto), Camugnano, Metropolitan City of Bologna, Emilia
data.meta_description: Ponte di Verzuno (Rio Rivaletto), Camugnano, Metropolitan City of Bologna, Emilia-Romagna, Italy : Small outcrop of hydrothermalites, associated to serpentinite, listvenite, chloritized gabbro pertaining to the ophiolitic suite.
